{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "山路又长又弯，运粮的人走得很辛苦。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "粮食要送到远处，普通车子在窄路上不好转弯，大家常常需要停下来休息。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "诸葛亮看在眼里，想找一个省力又安全的办法。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "他请工匠一起观察山路。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "有人量木轮的大小，有人试着推车，有人记录哪里容易卡住。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "诸葛亮说，好工具不是一下子想成的，要一边试，一边改进。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "几天后，大家做出一种木头载具，名字叫木牛流马。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "它有稳稳的木架和能转动的木轮，可以装粮食，也方便在小路上慢慢前进。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "孩子们看见模型，都觉得名字很有趣。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一次试用时，木架有点重，转弯也不够灵活。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "工匠没有灰心，又把木轮磨得更圆，把把手调到合适的位置。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "大家轮流试推，发现走起来比以前轻松多了。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "后来，木牛流马帮助队伍把粮食稳稳送到需要的地方。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "这个故事告诉我们，发明来自细心观察，也来自许多人一起动手。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "遇到难题时，动脑合作，常能找到新办法。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    }
  ]
}
